{"thig6.1:0.1":"Therigatha 6.1 ","thig6.1:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thig6.1:0.3":"Pancasatamattatherigatha ","thig6.1:1.1":"“Yassa maggam na janasi, ","thig6.1:1.2":"agatassa gatassa va; ","thig6.1:1.3":"Tam kuto cagatam sattam, ","thig6.1:1.4":"‘mama putto’ti rodasi. ","thig6.1:2.1":"Magganca khossa janasi, ","thig6.1:2.2":"agatassa gatassa va; ","thig6.1:2.3":"Na nam samanusocesi, ","thig6.1:2.4":"evamdhamma hi panino. ","thig6.1:3.1":"Ayacito tatagacchi, ","thig6.1:3.2":"nanunnato ito gato; ","thig6.1:3.3":"Kutoci nuna agantva, ","thig6.1:3.4":"vasitva katipahakam; ","thig6.1:3.5":"Itopi annena gato, ","thig6.1:3.6":"tatopannena gacchati. ","thig6.1:4.1":"Peto manussarupena, ","thig6.1:4.2":"samsaranto gamissati; ","thig6.1:4.3":"Yathagato tatha gato, ","thig6.1:4.4":"ka tattha paridevana”. ","thig6.1:5.1":"“Abbahi vata me sallam, ","thig6.1:5.2":"duddasam hadayassitam; ","thig6.1:5.3":"Ya me sokaparetaya, ","thig6.1:5.4":"puttasokam byapanudi. ","thig6.1:6.1":"Sajja abbulhasallaham, ","thig6.1:6.2":"Nicchata parinibbuta; ","thig6.1:6.3":"Buddham dhammanca sanghanca, ","thig6.1:6.4":"Upemi saranam munim”. ","thig6.1:7.1":"Ittham sudam pancasatamatta theri bhikkhuniyo … pe…. "}